cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with speech recognition using deep learning techniques. Additionally, it may also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with speech recognition. The paper also introduces novel techniques for training deep LSTMs, which may fall under the category of cs.LG (Learning) or cs.SI (Signal Processing). Finally, the paper proposes efficient algorithms for training these networks, which may also fall under the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
